    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at SRM University Holdings Services. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Senior Teacher to strengthen our Gwalior-based team.\n\nAbout SRM University Holdings Services:\nSRM University Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with SRM University Holdings Services!",
